{"title":"我的去除函数像座富士山","slug":"我的去除函数像座富士山","date":"2026-03-30T12:37:02.034Z","updated":"2026-03-30T12:39:42.537Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/我的去除函数像座富士山.json","excerpt":"**摘要**：   本文是一篇以娱乐为目的的改编文章，基于作者本科毕业设计《行星齿轮……的探究》的真实实验结果。研究通过“胡乱设计”开发了一款行星齿轮式抛光工具，其材料去除轮廓经归一化后呈现出类高斯型特征，但仿真结果与实际存在偏差。有趣的是，作者发现该去除函数轮廓与富士山高度相似，遂将其命名为“富士山型去除函数”。尽管该结果看似创新，但作者强调其核心作用仅为帮助自己顺利毕业，不具备学术价值或复现性，且研究过程缺乏严谨性。文章旨在调侃科研中形式主义与偶然性，并致谢母校SUSTech。","covers":["https://img.rubbish.press/file/2603/1774874321206_image.png","https://img.rubbish.press/file/2603/1774874339935_image.png","https://img.rubbish.press/file/2603/1774874350181_image.png"],"content":"<p>000<span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><msup><mrow></mrow><mrow><mn>1</mn><mo separator=\"true\">,</mo><mo>∗</mo></mrow></msup></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">^{1,*}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.8141em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span></span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.8141em;\"><span style=\"top:-3.063em;margin-right:0.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:2.7em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\">1</span><span class=\"mpunct mtight\">,</span><span class=\"mord mtight\">∗</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>，CityU在逃保安<span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><msup><mrow></mrow><mn>2</mn></msup></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">^{2}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.8141em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span><